Question: Are both the ball to the right of the other balls and the black helmet made of plastic?

Reference Answer: Yes, both the ball and the helmet are made of plastic.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n146522.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='ball')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='ball')
IMAGE1=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='black helmet')
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What material is the ball made of?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What material is the black helmet made of?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'plastic' and {ANSWER1} == 'plastic' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
